      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to hit the road! It runs smoothly and looks great too. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
