    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed with poly-bushing upgrades and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution translates to telepathic turn-in. All major preventative maintenance is current, including rod bearing service and shim-and-bucket valve adjustments, making this a mechanically robust example ready for the track or the canyon.",
