    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior boasts a lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor, expected stone chips from highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronic features\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive file of receipts included. Recent work includes a fresh fluid service and a new set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and provides a composed, quiet ride that inspires confidence. This is an excellent opportunity to own a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has clearly been the pride and joy of its previous owner.",
      "price": 34850.0,
