      "description": "This vehicle represents an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. Every aspect of this automobile has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards of mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. A premier choice for those seeking reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 36450.0,
