    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly such a gem. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and is in really solid shape, ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives beautifully and has plenty of life left in it. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been cared for with love, this is definitely the one for you. I've had so many great memories in this car\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
