      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing aluminum control arms and a rigid subframe for sharp turn-in and predictable lateral dynamics. Notable maintenance includes proactive replacement of the rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is within tight tolerances. This is a mechanically robust example that prioritizes performance and chassis feedback, offering an authentic analog driving experience.",
